{
  "text": "1 More generally, it could be a collection of reactions and chemical species indexed by an infinite set; this is necessary, e.g., to describe polymerization. A corresponding effect can be obtained within π-calculus [CITATION_1] , but here we consider only finite systems of reactions.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "59914705"
